분석1. 항공기 출발 지연 데이터 분석¶

1.sql처리¶
In [9]:
tic("depcount_by_month_by_year_sql")
depcount_by_month_by_year_sql =
sdf_sql(sc,"
           select year, month, count(*) as n 
              from ontime
              where depdelay > 30 and depdelay is not null
              group by year, month
              order by year, month           
          ") %>% collect()
toc()

2. dplyr 처리¶
In [10]:
tic("depcount_by_month_by_year_dplyr")
depcount_by_month_by_year_dplyr =
ontime_tbl %>% filter(!is.na(DepDelay)) %>% 
               filter(DepDelay>30) %>% 
               count(Year,Month) %>%      
               arrange(Year,Month) %>%
               collect()
toc()

3. Line plot 그래프 시각화¶
1)sql Data¶
In [11]:
library(repr)
options(repr.plot.width=10,repr.plot.height=3 )
depcount_by_month_by_year_sql %>% 
      mutate(year=factor(year))->plot_df

plot_df %>% 
 ggplot(aes(month, n, color=year))+geom_line() +
     scale_x_discrete(limits=1:12, labels=paste(1:12,"M"))
2)dplyr Data¶
In [12]:
options(repr.plot.width=10,repr.plot.height=3 )
depcount_by_month_by_year_dplyr %>% 
       mutate(Year=factor(Year))%>% 
       ggplot(aes(Month, n, color=Year))+geom_line() +
       scale_x_discrete(limits=1:12, labels=paste(1:12,"M"))
